metadata.description: Eddie is just another kid on the street-a little shy, a little gangly, a little meek-until he crosses the path of a local street tough named Pete. And that’s when Pete decides to turn the bookish “Superboy’s” life around in Realworlds: Superman, the newest Prestige one-shot exploring the real-life influence exerted by the DC Universe’s most iconic characters.
metadata.name: Realworlds
